data.description: Beautifully appointed William Lyan Single Story energy efficient home with 4 Bedroom plus den and a Casita that has a 3/4 Bath in a Resort Style Golf Course Community. Mountain falls has a Clubhouse, Chef style restaurant on the lake, golf course w/driving range, jogging/walking trails, exercise room, 3 pools, spa, etc. Open Living room, kitchen, dining room w/ granite counters and eat-in kitchen island, tile and hardwood flooring, Granite Wet Bar, primary suite with make-up nook, his and her huge walk-in closets, beautifully landscaped front and backyard. Den could be a 5th bedroom w/double doors and Casita could be a guest quarters, in-law suite, etc. All electric with only power bill being minimal ($40 with the $272 solar bill). This home has everything you need!  Solar easily transferred and very cooperative.
